Hello [~topener],

Are you still having this issue? If still getting same issue please follow the below instruction :

*Step one:* Uninstall your SDK by using {code}
appc ti sdk uninstall (SDK version ){code}

*Step two:* Then reinstall the Latest version SDK, do so from the command line: {code}appc ti sdk install latest
or
appc ti sdk install (SDK version ){code}

If above instruction will not work for you, please let us know and provide your logs with details working environment. Thanks.
